Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去上驾校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let it rip, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.09,0:01:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不错  好搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad, partner in crime
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过面包再烤焦一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The toasts could have been a little darker, though
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  要去捉水母了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, want to go jelly fishing?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天得上学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have school today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上学了  我一整天要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do all day while you're at school?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.53,0:01:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我走了的时候  你一般会干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you normally do when I'm gone?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for you to get back
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.57,0:01:48.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你跟我一起上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:48.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come to school with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟我一起上学  当同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and me in school together as classmates
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想就快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:57.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(544,936)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brace yourself, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由我来为你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm about to introduce you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一生所见最为惊险刺激的学术之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the greatest academic thrill ride of your lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:09.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(886,202)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不用排队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no line
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星请看  学习之走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold, Patrick, the hallway of learning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是学习之饮水机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:16.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's the fountain of learning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是学习之柜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these are the lockers of learning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是学习之阶梯  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And these are the stairs of learning, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  普通的楼梯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, they're just the stairs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是学习之阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are the stairs of learning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.99,0:02:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其他同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's everyone?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.02,0:02:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概都在家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home probably
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九点才上课
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Class doesn't start till 9:00
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六点二十
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,6:20?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是说要迟到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I thought you said you were late
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早到快迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Late for being early
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么时候戴的表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When did I start wearing a watch?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.07,0:02:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在参观上课用的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the room with the most class
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the classroom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边是黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's the chalkboard
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.57,0:02:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以为我们取一瓢知识之饮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the ladle that helps us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,drink from the fountain of knowledge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腹中经纶有多少  全都记录在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And those drinks are recorded here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:03:00.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,196)}好榜样
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个好榜样光荣榜上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the Good Noodles Board
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.81,0:02:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:02:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:05.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(406,326)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attendance
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笔迹工整
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Penmanship
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,基本课桌卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Basic Desk Sanitation
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进阶课桌卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Advanced Desk Sanitation
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.95,0:03:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你把名字写上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll add your name
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你也就能集到好榜样之星了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can start collecting good noodle stars, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,704)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你星星好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all the stars you have
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的高度我肯定达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never be that good
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟大家没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just like everyone else
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星星有多少无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no matter how many stars I have
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七十四颗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seventy-four
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was it him?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是洛哥  班级科学项目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Roger, our class science project
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他能教什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does he teach us?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最伟大的一课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The greatest lesson of all
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生命珍贵的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the precious value of life
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋壳洛哥代表着一条脆弱的界限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roger Shell represents the fragile line
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分隔着船上司机的生与死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,between life and death when behind the wheel of a boat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这盏灯泡代表着知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This lightbulb represents knowledge
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡它不再发光发热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And without its energy and warmth
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洛哥几分钟不到就会没命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,within minutes, Roger would die
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.30,0:03:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生  死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life, death
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.99,0:03:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生  死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life, death
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生  死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life, death
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.24,0:03:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生  死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life, death
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生  死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life, death
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早到最棒的优点就在于
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The best part of being early is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以坐前排  靠近老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you get to sit close to the teacher
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二把椅子坐不坐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think you can handle the second chair?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会特别棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be great
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, class
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之所以会自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the only reason I say that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为我们班来了一位新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is because I see we have a new student
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学  请你站起来自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Young man, why don't you stand up and introduce yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那胖小孩跟谁说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's the fat kid talking to?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是跟你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,she's the teacher
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  把你的名字告诉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, tell the class your name
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be nervous
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是想知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just want to know your name
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十四
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twenty-four
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  又一个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, another genius
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are they laughing?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间刚刚好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it's just in the timing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天的第一课是拐弯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's first lesson will be on "Turning"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十四
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twenty-four
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了比二十四更好笑的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought of something funnier than 24
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me hear it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二十五
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同学  鉴于你第一天上课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Young man, this is your first day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只给你个警告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I'll let you off with a warning
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至于你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As for you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好榜样要起带头作用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I expect more from a good noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认真听课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay attention
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  拐弯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, then, "Turning":
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,170)}红灯下拐弯
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每位司机的必备知识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what every driver should know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拐弯时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you are turning
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少十分有必要打出转向信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it is important to signal at least
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1132,394)}胖冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598,908)}便便
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胖冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Big Fat Meanie"?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you can't do that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她可是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's the teacher
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about the teacher?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.87,0:05:59.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:05:59.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(922,228)}胖冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(438,820)}便便
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得好像我真长这样似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As if I really look like this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你一定知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I believe you know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.67,0:06:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两次扰乱课堂有什么惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the punishment for two classroom disruptions
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:24.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,200)}好榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:24.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,352)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.92,0:06:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是想当好榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but if one wishes to be a good noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须有个好榜样的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one must behave like a good noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是好榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a good noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是好榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a good noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现好了再还你星星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll get this star back when you earn it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nooo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.42,0:06:45.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:45.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  现在是睡觉时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, is it nap time?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  受不了你这样闹来闹去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I've had enough of your nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东西收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now collect your things
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.10,0:06:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搬到教室后排那张空座去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and move to the available desk in the back of the room
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.04,0:06:59.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:06:59.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胖冬瓜要你搬就搬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because the Big Fat Meanie said so
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真谢谢你了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐后排还是能当个好榜样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I could be a good noodle from back here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前说到  左转必须要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, as I was saying, when turning left, you must
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so hard to hear
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底什么样的同学才会坐这后排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of student sits back here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1078,656)}傻子才上学
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别理他  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just ignore him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, over here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管干什么都别看他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟你说个事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to tell you something
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说个大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something important
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许现在正好适合下课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this would be a good time for recess
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,课上可搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny stuff in there
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上课闹的事一点都不好笑  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is nothing funny
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,about what you did in there, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都害我惹上麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我搬到教室后排去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me moved to the back of the room
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我一颗好榜样之星没了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cost me one of my good noodle stars
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一笨星星谁羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who cares about a stupid star?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  貌似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Patrick, it seems like
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可羡慕笨星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you would care a lot about stupid stars
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你本来就是笨星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,considering you are one
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下课就找你算账
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with you after class
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is after class
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.55,0:08:51.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:51.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看到谁打架啊  你有看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see anyone fighting, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们是在说我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're talking about us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.03,0:08:55.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在打架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:55.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're fighting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if I do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fight
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尬死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.27,0:09:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟海绵宝宝在打架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and I were fighting
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fighting?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't believe I'm saying this, but
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.16,0:09:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我要处分你跟你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Squarepants, I hereby
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sentence you and your friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留校察看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to detention
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留校察看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Detention?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.72,0:09:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿海神王宽恕你们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May Neptune have mercy on your soul
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好榜样才一天就变反面教材了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In one day I've gone from good noodle to bad egg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是笨蛋派大星的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all stupid Patrick's fault
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我更恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate you more
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不管怎样我都要恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd hate you no matter what
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.28,0:09:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我不恨你  我也要恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well I'd hate you even if I didn't hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算你刚说的有逻辑  我也要恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd hate you even if that made sense
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算你是我  我也要恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd hate you even if you were me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就这么恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how much I hate you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要恨你  就算是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd hate you if even, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.35,0:10:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算让洛哥活命的灯泡灭了我也恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd hate you even if the lightbulb
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,keeping Roger alive went out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.85,0:10:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉叫你笨星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I called you a stupid star
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你惹上了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I got you in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害你搬到了教室后排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and got you moved to the back of class
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害你好榜样之星没了一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and got your good noodle star removed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还朝你吐纸团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and shot spitballs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉你的抱歉太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry your apology is so long
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.29,0:10:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去救洛哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's save Roger
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我帮他保温
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll keep him warm
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到储物间里拿灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you get a lightbulb from the supply closet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(924,278)}储物间
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lightbulb
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1158,856)}灯泡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怎么非得放这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But why does it have to be so far away?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己给洛哥保温
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to go find Roger some warmth
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lightbulb
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不保温洛哥会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without its warmth, Roger will die
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洛哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roger
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.12,0:11:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,灯泡也没什么好保温的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the lightbulb will have nothing to warm
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们救活了洛哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We saved Roger's life
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.22,0:11:53.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在单向黑板后面看到了整个经过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:53.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw the whole thing from behind my one-way chalkboard
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴能看到你们齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't be happier with your teamwork
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.15,0:12:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要给你们俩都奖励一颗金色小星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:12:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've decided to give you each one gold star
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道救活一颗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Although, I'm not sure what saving an egg
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟滑浪学校有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has to do with boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滑浪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boating school?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为这是在上西班牙语课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought this was Spanish class
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  胖冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you, Big Fat Meanie
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错过了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.72,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,354)\pos(734,214)}蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz27.79\pos(345.802,508)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:27.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
