Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.1\pos(485.802,720)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,494)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534,224)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你更喜欢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you like better?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚碎块还是牡蛎脆皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The coral bits or the nacho oyster skins?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like neither
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那藤壶圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about the barnacle rings?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are they any good?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What will you have?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得海草
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's your vote on the kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  就这么直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, let's just get this out of the way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜单上的餐我都讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate everything on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝珊瑚碎块
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try the coral bits
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就尝尝珊瑚碎块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try the coral bits
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be one dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是什么傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something stupid, I'm sure
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别肮脏的一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A very dirty dollar?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我赚到的第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my one millionth dollar earned
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.72,0:13:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每只螃蟹的蟹生目标就是赚到一百万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every Krab's goal in life is to make a million dollars
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我赚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I got mine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚把我赚的第一百万块钱给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have just given me my one millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么奖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I win?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:58.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.20,0:13:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:13:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody get out
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们坏了我的好心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're spoiling my moment
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该高兴点  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulate yourselves, lads
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船长没了忠诚的船员  就什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A captain's nothing without his loyal crew
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这样的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, a crew like you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许一生就只能遇见一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,comes along maybe once in a lifetime
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了奖励你们帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to reward you for helping me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赚到了我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make my millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要带你们去旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you on a trip
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A trip
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去哪  奢华泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we going, Fancy Spring?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,荣宠岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pamper Island?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再猜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头民俗村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom Folk Village
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比那强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better than that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钓蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clam fishing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,累死累活就这么个奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the reward we get for all our hard work?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.61,0:14:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在脏湖乘臭船钓臭蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fishing for stinky clams
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a smelly old boat on a filthy lagoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(378,778)}小气鬼号
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你管这叫快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call this fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on now, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们三个出海闲着没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three fellas at sea with nothing to do
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就来垂钓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but throw their lines in the water
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钓几只蛤蜊再丢回水里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,catch a few clams and then throw them back
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不觉得很快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that's fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个时候我本来还能戴假发套的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to think I could be wearing a powdered wig right now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  想不想要我在这边下钩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, you want me to cast out over here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你尽情观赏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can watch me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你就到那边下钩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you cast out over there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我尽情无视你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can ignore you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挥杆小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're swinging that
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,be careful with
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've had enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward, you got to lighten up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然那小子钓得是有点热情过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, the lad's a bit overeager
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你一定要学着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you've got to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从容应对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to roll with the punches
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go with the flow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且上船最好别乱带东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't bring anything on the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然可容易丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you ain't prepared to lose
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.45,0:15:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:15:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你挥杆钩到了我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you hooked me millionth dollar on the back swing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉回来  不然我惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reel it in before I keelhaul ya
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.88,0:16:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  快拉回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, quick, reel it in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听到音乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear the music?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可是固定反复的四四拍D小调弦乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a 4/4 string ostinato in D minor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水手都知道那意味着死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every sailor knows that means death
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁早拉回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reel it in before it's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐越奏越快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The music's getting faster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你们了  一群坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, you stinking bilge rats
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别奏乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop playing that music
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托别奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it, please
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算我求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油啊  钱钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, honey
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can make it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Swim faster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来我这儿  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to me, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here she comes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, please
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She made it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚才差点以为钱要没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For a second or two, I thought she was a goner
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快不  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, some trip, hey, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说来你们肯定不信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're never going to believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只巨型蓝唇蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A giant blue-lipped clam
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃了我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ate me millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钱没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost me dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且再也拿不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll never get it back
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回不来  回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never, never
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没见过蟹老板这么崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen Mr. Krabs so broken up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, please
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯是他爱演罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's such a drama queen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别演了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drop the act
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.63,0:17:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  才一块臭钱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, it's just a stupid dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天有眼  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For Pete's sake, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想开点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,suck it up
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就帮你把钱找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll help you get your dollar back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait right here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得来认真钓蛤蜊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's where clam fishing gets serious
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们负责钓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, you boys man the fishing poles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我负责寻找蓝唇蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll keep me eyes peeled for Old Blue Lip
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Captain
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  要想走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And remember, we don't leave
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得先抓到蛤蜊  把钱救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until we catch that clam and rescue me dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.27,0:18:40.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:40.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finished
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都漂流三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been here for three days
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果一点进展都没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and haven't gotten a nibble
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没戏唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.75,0:18:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还得回家喂小蜗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've got to get home to feed Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我们就要死在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to die out here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全怪有只蛤蜊吃了蟹老板的臭钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just because a clam ate Mr. Krabs' stupid dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真想救回他的钱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if he wants his dollar back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就给他钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we give it to him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.03,0:19:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Know what I mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看咱发现啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what we got
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't me millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一普普通通的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is an ordinary dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍微皱了点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's been crumpled up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有点破  泡了湖水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:42.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,torn slightly, soaked in the lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面还有半光泽珊瑚蓝二号的口红印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and kissed with Coral Blue Number Two
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Semi-gloss Lipstick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实是珊瑚蓝三号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's Coral Blue Number Three
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这么信任你们  却给了我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I trusted you, and you gave me this
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.27,0:19:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己的员工竟然会这样背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe me own crew would betray me like this
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.31,0:20:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.29,0:20:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦情戏没法动摇我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will not be swayed by tears anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就只能玩奖励这套了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I have no choice but to offer a reward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是又能出来垂钓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it another fishing trip?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这个三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's this sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sandwich?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.80,0:20:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然要我为了个三明治拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You expect me to break my back over a sandwich?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是随便什么三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这个三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船上可是还有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got plenty more to
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eat
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下想必能相互理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I think we understand each other
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.65,0:20:41.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:41.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody eats
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先救回我第一百万块钱再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I get my millionth dollar back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.92,0:20:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跟你说句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.63,0:20:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板已经完全失去理智了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Mr. Krabs has gone completely insane?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(390,966)}逝者安息\N我的第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他都失去跟自己最亲近的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's lost something near and dear to him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do we get out of here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要完全没动静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we're real quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能溜到救生船上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we can sneak over to the lifeboat
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.82,0:21:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说  你们以为自己能躲过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you thought you'd skip out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹的法眼  是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on old Krabs, did you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.87,0:21:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可是保证过要帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even after you promised to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你们的小心思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what you're thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一块臭钱而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"It's just a dumb old dollar"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接抛弃那个老头子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Let's just leave the old man"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.05,0:21:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他发现不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"He won't notice"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not going down like that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.25,0:21:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这样暗算我的员工就一个用途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one use for a backstabbing crew like you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,live bait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛤蜊这么久不来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If that clam didn't come before
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪来的自信觉得现在会来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what makes you think he'll come now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll come
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, listen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整天跟海绵宝宝一块工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I work with SpongeBob all day long
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以下面要说的这句话我非常熟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I know what I'm talking about when I say
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.37,0:22:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你完完全全疯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you are completely out of your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来  有新鲜的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, fresh meat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep thrashing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He likes it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.35,0:22:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,closer
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.51,0:22:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,物归原主了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一百万块钱终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got me millionth dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:00.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远离我们而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gone forever out of our lives
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.19,0:23:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么死的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't it have been me?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.12,0:23:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么死的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't it have been you?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.50,0:23:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么他会这样牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to go like this?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么他会这样牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to go like this
Dialogue: 1,0:23:14.55,0:23:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我跟这白痴绑在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave me tied to this idiot?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.16,0:23:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.97,0:23:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you boys met
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.45,0:23:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一百万块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me millionth dollar?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.17,0:23:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么搞回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you get it back?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.92,0:23:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝唇蛤蜊挺能打的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Blue Lips is quite the fighter
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.15,0:23:37.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们最后达成了交易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:37.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so eventually, we settled on a trade
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.92,0:23:38.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿什么交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:38.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you give him?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.36,0:23:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing important
